PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1991-2053, which authorized the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION and the DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC WORKS to finalize a number of real estate transactions involving the site of the CANADIAN MUSEUM OF CIVILIZATION in Hull, Quebec, by revoking Schedules "B" to "F" to that Order and substituting corrected ones therefor.
